MemoryMap::MapElement::Anonymous

MemoryMap::MapElement::Anonymous Class Reference

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Reference counter for anonymous mappings.

The buffer for anonymous mappings is allocated and freed by this class rather than the user. Anonymous mappings are indicated by a non-null pointer.
